                        script#template-com-slider(type='text/html').
                            <h5>Slider</h5>
                            <p>Wolmart provides a powerful slider component, using <a href="https://swiperjs.com/swiper-api" target="_blank">Swiper</a>, the famous touch enabled, fast &amp; responsive jQuery plugin. Before using it, we recommend to read <a href="#template-com-grid" class="document-link">grid spacing</a>, in order to perform <b>first paint</b> earlier, we display non-interactive carousel with css. It becomes interactive after javascript is executed.</p>
                            <h6>Example: Products slider in 4 columns</h6>
                            <p>Custom swiper options could be given in <code>data-swiper-options</code> attribute in html  .</p>
                            <pre>
                            .swiper-container swiper-theme(data-swiper-options=`
                                {
                                    'slidesPerView': 2,
                                    'loop': false,          // Here, we display slider with <code>row</code> <code>cols-2</code> <code>cols-md-3</code>
                                    'spaceBetween': 20,     // <code>cols-lg-4</code> classes at first, these classes will be
                                    'breakpoints': {        // removed when slider is initialized by javascript.
                                        '768': {
                                            'slidesPerView': 3
                                        },
                                        '992': {
                                            'slidesPerView': 4
                                        }
                                    },
                                    'navigation': {
                                        'nextEl': '.swiper-button-next',
                                        'prevEl': '.swiper-button-prev',
                                    }
                                }`)
                                .swiper-wrapper.row.cols-2.cols-md-3.cols-lg-4
                                    .swiper-slide
                                    ...
                                button.swiper-button.swiper-button-prev
                                button.swiper-button.swiper-button-next
                                .swiper-pagination
                            </pre>
                            <h6>Helper classes</h6>
                            <table class="table">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr><th>Class</th><th>Description</th></tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr><td><code>nav-inner</code><code>nav-top</code></td><td>Place nav inner, top.</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td><code>pg-white</code><code>pg-grey</code></td><td>Make pagination bullets white or grey.</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td><code>pg-inner</code></td><td>Place pagination inner.</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td><code>shadow-swiper</code></td><td>Allow slider to show items' shadow.</td></tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
